(admin 'CREATE NAMESPACE test')

!admin 'CREATE DEFERRED VIEW test::v { id: Int4 } AS { FROM [{ id: 1 }] }'
---
> Error FLOW_008
>   Flow requires at least one source
>
> HELP
>   A view flow must read from a table, view, ring buffer, or series. Inline data (FROM [...]) cannot be used as the source for a view.
>
